<h1>Articles</h1>

Our blog has <%= Article.public_count %> articles and counting!
<p>Article often refers to:

Article (grammar), a grammatical element used to indicate definiteness or indefiniteness
Article (publishing), a piece of nonfictional prose that is an independent part of a publication</p>

<h2>There are some articles you definately read , update content and also delete article.</h2>
<ul>
  <% @articles.each do |article| %>
    <% unless article.archived? %>
      <li>
        <%= link_to article.title, article %>
      </li>
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<h2>Click on below link to make your own new article.</h2>
<%= link_to "New Article", new_article_path %>
